{"word":"πωλοδαμνέω","slug":"πωλοδαμνέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πωλοδαμνέω</b></el> <el>(πωλοδαμνέω,) ( φυτ. <el>-ήσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to break young horses</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to train up</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:πωλοδάμνης'><el>πωλοδάμνης</el></a>\n"}]}